Annotation 1 [src]:
Character Entities for XHTML This is the XML Schema Character Entities module for XHTML This module declares the set of character entities for XHTML, including the Latin 1, Symbol and Special character collections. XML Schema does not support Entities, hence Entities are enable through an Internal DTD Subset. $Id$

decimal conversions of the ISO 10646 values and refer to the
document character set. Names are Unicode [UNICODE] names.
